    "TSF and RISE had usability improvements.",
    "HC1 is designed to be contractable, in that you can specify a maximum train time.",
    "In 2021, HIVE-COTE was again updated to further address scalability issues and reflect recent innovations to individual TSC representations and HIVE-COTE v2.0 (HC2) (Middlehurst et al. 2021) was proposed.",
    "In HC2, RISE, TSF and cBOSS are replaced, with only STC retained.",
    "TDE (Middlehurst et al. 2020b) replaces cBOSS as the dictionary classifier."
